# Esercizio Punto 1 
testo = '''
Day after day, day after day,
We stuck, nor breath nor motion;
As idle as a painted ship
Upon a painted ocean.

Water, water, every where,
And all the boards did shrink;
Water, water, every where,
Nor any drop to drink.

The very deep did rot: O Christ!
That ever this should be!
Yea, slimy things did crawl with legs
Upon the slimy sea.

About, about, in reel and rout
The death-fires danced at night;
The water, like a witch's oils,
Burnt green, and blue and white.
'''

# Definisco la funzione di conteggio 
def conteggio_righe(testo):
    # divide il testo in righe differenti, per non leggerlo come se fosse un'unica stringa
    righe = testo.splitlines()

    conteggio = 0

    #il loop assicura che vengano contate tutte le righe 
    for riga in righe:
        # questo permette di scartare le righe vuote
        if riga. strip():
            conteggio += 1 
    return conteggio     

 
print(conteggio_righe(testo))